data.description: Welcome to your new home in the heart of Fort Caroline! Enjoy the enchanting Florida evenings on your covered lanai, perfect for unwinding with family and friends. The house features tile throughout, offering a practical and stylish solution for easy maintenance. The open floor plan seamlessly integrates the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The well-appointed kitchen provides ample space for culinary adventures, equipped plenty of storage for all your cooking essentials. Both bedrooms are generously sized, providing an abundance of space for relaxation and personalization. With natural light streaming in through large windows, these rooms offer a tranquil sanctuary for rest and rejuvenation. Located in the coveted area of Fort Caroline, this home offers not only a tranquil retreat but also convenient access to local amenities, schools, and parks. Embrace the opportunity to make this beautiful house your new home, where every day feels like a vacation.
